<p>20 July 1915<br/>Tuesday</p>
<p>At work today on the water works splendid advancements being made<br/>Weather very hot   &amp;  Sultry<br/>We "Stand to arms" at 3 a.m.<br/>The period of the Mohamedan Ramadan is at present in force   &amp;  our people are expecting trouble.</p>
<p>1915 July 21<br/>Wednesday</p>
<p>Terracing again<br/>The valley is nearly finished now   &amp; we expect to start in another part next shift<br/>Turks fire twenty shells at our aeroplane without getting near it</p>
